OCI Asked to Comment on Share Buyback, Order Speculation

-- B y   S h i n h y e   K a n g
-- 
2011-09-20T02:52:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-20/oci-asked-to-comment-on-share-buyback-order-speculation.html
OCI Co., a polysilicon maker, was
asked by the Korea exchange to comment on speculation it may buy
back shares and may win an order for the material used in solar
cells, according to a regulatory filing today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Shinhye Kang at 
 skang24@bloomberg.net  